  "reviews": [
    {
      "name": "Cahya Saraswati",
      "rating": 5,
      "text": "Tempatnya luas, banyak pilihan area untuk indoor dan outdoor dan kids friendly karena ada playground. Suasana sangat nyaman dan pelayanan ramah. Porsi makanan cukup besar, waktu tunggu makanan relatif singkat dan harga yg sesuai.\n\nOverall very recommended :))",
      "when": "4 bulan lalu",
      "images": [
        "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1dl-fKQUMUZ9rFSmm13BX-40kuuO0DTFzpsMf_C6vhoqSVNrKJnceOF-nhXx9SB1wfqpNtp7UfjbDT4AQmRveStMr_8sEmGRnFg5ZzxfPvv0hqwksAfmUfO2nt6MKdWn-KM6usji1pzIk=k-no",
